    <div class="row">   
    	<div class="col-sm-8">
			<h1>Navigation</h1>
			<div class="breakout">
			Navigation elements are used within the MyService header, footer and process flows. Animated sliding panels are used for log in, for help during a process flow, and to access information on 24hr counselling and support services. Other global navigation elements include a 'Return to top' button.
			</div>
			
			<h2>Header</h2>
			
			<p>There are three styling options used in the MyService header:</p>
			<ol>
				<li><b><a href="#default-header">Default header</a></b>. The default header style.</li>
				<li><b><a href="#reduced-header">Reduced header</a></b>. A lighter and compact version of the default header.</li>
				<li><b><a href="#light-header">Light header</a></b>. Used only for the unauthenticated homepage.</li>
				
			</ol>
			
			<a name="default-header"></a>
			<h3>Default header</h3>
			<p>This style is used for all pages across MyService <i>except</i> those that sit within a process flow (eg. making a claim for initial liability).</p>
			<div class="example-box">
				<h6>EXAMPLE</h6>
				<table>
					<tr><td>
						<header class="uikit-header" style="width:100%;">
						  <div class="container" style="width:100%;">
							  <h1>MyService<sup class="beta large">Beta</sup></h1>
							  <button class="toggle" aria-expanded="false">Menu</button>
							  <ul class="menu">
								<li><a class="header-home" href="index-claims">Home</a></li>
								<li><a class="header-profile" href="/profile">My profile</a></li>
							  </ul>
						  </div>
						</header>		
					</td></tr>
					<tr><td class="example-code">
						<code>&lt;header class="uikit-header"&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;div class="container"&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;h1&gt;MyService&lt;sup class="beta large"&gt;Beta&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;button class="toggle" aria-expanded="false"&gt;Menu&lt;/button&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;ul class="menu"&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="header-home" href="index-claims"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="header-profile" href="/profile"&gt;My profile&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;/ul&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;/div&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;/header&gt;</code><br>
					</td></tr>
				</table>
			</div>
			
			<a name="reduced-header"></a>
			<h3>Reduced header</h3>
			<p>This header style is used for pages that sit within a process flow (eg. making a claim for initial liability).</p>
			<div class="example-box">
				<h6>EXAMPLE</h6>
				<table>
					<tr><td>
						<header class="uikit-header reduced-header" style="width:100%;">
						  <div class="container" style="width:100%;">
							  <h1>MyService<sup class="beta large">Beta</sup></h1>
						  </div>
						</header>		
					</td></tr>
					<tr><td class="example-code">
						<code>&lt;header class="uikit-header reduced-header"&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;div class="container"&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;h1&gt;MyService&lt;sup class="beta large"&gt;Beta&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;/div&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;/header&gt;</code><br>
					</td></tr>
				</table>
			</div>
			
			<a name="light-header"></a>
			<h3>Light header</h3>
			<p>This header style is used for the unathenticated homepage. That is, the page a user will see before they login to MyService.</p>
			<div class="example-box">
				<h6>EXAMPLE</h6>
				<table>
					<tr><td>
						<header class="uikit-header landing-page" style="width:100%;">
							<div class="container" style="width:100%;">
								<img src="docs/images/logo-dva-black.svg" alt="Department of Veteran's Affairs logo" />
								<h1>MyService<sup class="beta large">Beta</sup></h1>
								<p class="header-login"><a href="#" class="panel-btn">Log in</a>/</p>
							</div>
						</header>		
					</td></tr>
					<tr><td class="example-code">
						<code>&lt;header class="uikit-header landing-page"&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;div class="container"&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;img src="docs/images/logo-dva-black.svg" alt="Department of Veteran's Affairs logo" /&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;h1&gt;MyService&lt;sup class="beta large"&gt;Beta&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;p class="header-login"&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="panel-btn"&gt;Log in&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;/p&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;/div&gt;</code><br>
						<code>&lt;/header&gt;</code><br>
					</td></tr>
				</table>
			</div>
			
			<hr>
			
