			<h2>'Return to top' button</h2>
			<p>The <font color="red">#return-to-top</font> class is applied to an <code><font color="red">&lt;a href="javascript"&gt;</font></code> element to create the 'Return to top' button, visible on vertical scroll in the bottom-right of every page across MyService.</p>
			
			<hr>
			
		</div>
